All commit messages must follow Conventional Commits format:

type(scope?): subject

Allowed types:

- feat
- fix
- docs
- style
- refactor
- perf
- test
- build
- ci
- chore
- revert

Rules:

- Header maximum length: 200 characters
- Subject must NOT be:
  - UPPER CASE
  - PascalCase
  - Start Case
- Scope is optional
- Multiple scopes allowed using "/", "\" or ","
- Use sentence case for subject

Examples:

✔️ Valid:
feat(auth): add email verification flow
fix(queue): prevent duplicate appointment ids
docs(readme): update setup instructions

❌ Invalid:
FEAT: ADD LOGIN
Fix: Update Stuff
feat: Add New Feature
